message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your endeavors. Given its exceptional value and quality, it is worth $12000 to you. Considering its worth and the potential it holds for you, I am offering it to you for $10000. This is a special offer tailored to appreciate your interest and commitment to excellence. Please let me know if this proposal meets your expectations or if there's any way I can assist you further.
